/**
 * data.el.js — Greek (Ελληνικά) content layer for the Problem Atlas.
 *
 * Overrides only the high-reach text fields per problem: name, stat,
 * trend.text, and the misconception. Everything language-neutral
 * (id, emoji, category, evidence ratings, sources) stays in data.js.
 * Merged by id. First-pass translation — Panos (native speaker) should
 * review before heavy promotion; figures mirror the audited English.
 *
 * Deep prose (scale/causes/interventions/actions) is intentionally not
 * yet translated — the Greek pages present the translated summary and
 * link into the full interactive app.
 */
